{"tid":527684,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"馮檢基當年幫保皇狗𠝹票，唔想佢出選就星期日初選投姚松炎","createTime":"2018-01-13T03:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T13:55:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f750b61d39f16e55cf8d918c3819d5a9bdb99c09","tid":527684,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:08:24.000Z","msg":"時事台post轉過嚟：<br />\n[url]馮檢基於泛民初選投票日將提供免費穿梭巴士來回票站 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/527403/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/527403/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n當年最後議席何君堯只用35657票入局，<br />\n<br />\n落敗的李卓人有30149票，馮檢基亦有17872票，兩者相加已有48021票，可以取代何君堯。<br />\n而2012年選舉時，李卓人其實坐擁40967票。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">明知何君堯係中聯辦人<br />\n點解一直喺九西出選嘅馮檢基會去勝算較低嘅新西出選?</span><br />\n<br />\n今日，學保皇一車車旅遊巴廢老票隊姚松炎，分分鐘仲有保皇暗票加持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/105826_a32d0999352072264cf573e49d0a4f6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F105826_a32d0999352072264cf573e49d0a4f6e.png&h=1897f6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬼到爆<br />\n就算唔係姚xx支持者,姚點都好過佢啩（至少之前有同本土研合作屌鳩政府土地政策）<br />\n點都唔好俾哩條垃圾出選<br />\n都應該隊死哩條廢老先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b089cdb5223bb8fcbfc4341874a410111e7d31","tid":527684,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:12:05.000Z","msg":"票站詳請：<br />\n[#九龍西 地方選區]<br />\n1.  #基督教協進大樓地窖 (尖沙咀加連威老道33號 ) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/VvtbyBGF8ty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FVvtbyBGF8ty&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2638d10e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/VvtbyBGF8ty</a><br />\n2.  #石硤尾邨展覽廳 (石硤尾南昌街215號石硤尾社區會堂側) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/35zWGst7dqr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2F35zWGst7dqr&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6fb1c93a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/35zWGst7dqr</a><br />\n3.  #黃埔港鐵站A出口對出空地 (近民兆街) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/BSVx8moBUPD2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FBSVx8moBUPD2&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c6b0fcb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/BSVx8moBUPD2</a><br />\n<br />\n[#新界東 地方選區]<br />\n1.  #粉嶺港鐵站A2出口地面空地 (粉嶺車站路) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/f9Qrhs73N8L2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2Ff9Qrhs73N8L2&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2b803af6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/f9Qrhs73N8L2</a><br />\n2.  #大埔墟街市及熟食中心旁邊空地 (大埔運頭街) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/WAzR5oy43F72\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FWAzR5oy43F72&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=3554d3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/WAzR5oy43F72</a><br />\n3.  #將軍澳港鐵站A2出口旁邊空地 (近寶邑路) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/q5Kk1xDbpDJ2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2Fq5Kk1xDbpDJ2&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e83ef999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/q5Kk1xDbpDJ2</a><br />\n4.  #大圍港鐵站D出口對出空地 (近富嘉花園) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/1MAR1DJFZXm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2F1MAR1DJFZXm&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c0da8d7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/1MAR1DJFZXm</a><br />\n5.  #香港中文大學鄭裕彤樓地下 <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/qbQMjDhKiuP2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FqbQMjDhKiuP2&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=688d5079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/qbQMjDhKiuP2</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">帶身份證 ,過去一年內嘅住址證明一份 </span></strong>"},{"pid":"87daa9c98420e9bfc48662946f2682aa1dd169f1","tid":527684,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:13:22.000Z","msg":"泛民初選實體投票日 1月14日（日）09:00-21:00 (記得去投票表態)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得等帶同身分證、2017年住址證明（銀行信件、政府公函或公用服務單據）去投票。<br />\n<br />\n投票日期：2018年1月14日（日）<br />\n投票時間：09:00-21:00"},{"pid":"cb4377e29a399cb849d9e43f7fa0d68fa316470f","tid":527684,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"泛民初選實體投票日 1月14日（日）09:00-21:00     (記得去投票表態)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/526439/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/526439/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1d2c1cbbc13ad07cf0e67d2c31723b2b1b95702f","tid":527684,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a5d77948ec250628ad27c7cd9b9b58476be888","tid":527684,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95f0800b6edd85313e90189608787787c82964e","tid":527684,"uid":28287,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:58:15.000Z","msg":"初你老母西咩 選選選 一日到黑都為撚左個濕鳩位關鍵一席 我屌你老母啦"},{"pid":"7f032191a907711f4b0b0bce6b56ae7faf28a05e","tid":527684,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d95f0800b6edd85313e90189608787787c82964e","tid":527684,"uid":28287,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T15:58:15.000Z","msg":"初你老母西咩 選選選 一日到黑都為撚左個濕鳩位關鍵一席 我屌你老母啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"有講